<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VUCAOFOODS | Potraviny Košíře</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --vucao-black: #1d1d1f;
            --vucao-gray: #86868b;
            --star-gold: #ffcc00;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: var(--vucao-black);
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        /* --- HLAVIČKA --- */
        header {
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f2f2;
        }
        .logo { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1px; text-transform: uppercase; }

        /* --- SLIDER ZNAČEK --- */
        .brands-section { padding: 40px 0; overflow: hidden; background: #fafafa; }
        .brands-title { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #a0a0a0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        .slider-track {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: max-content;
            animation: scroll 35s linear infinite;
        }
        .partner-item { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 30px; white-space: nowrap; }
        .separator { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #ddd; transform: rotate(45deg); margin-left: 60px; }

        /* Styly značek */
        .vilgain { color: #e30613; font-weight: 900; font-size: 22px; text-transform: lowercase; }
        .sufan { color: #3d2b1f; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .druid { color: #008631; font-weight: 900; font-size: 20px; }
        .gingles { color: #000; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 4px; }
        .vinarstvi { color: #6b0f1a; font-family: serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
        .prosekarna { color: #c5a059; font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 4px; }

        @keyframes scroll { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

        /* --- RECENZE --- */
        .reviews-section { padding: 60px 0; }
        .rating-summary { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .rating-summary h2 { font-size: 48px; margin: 0; }
        
        .reviews-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .review-card {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #efefef;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .review-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .stars { color: var(--star-gold); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
        .review-text { font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .reviewer { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #f9f9f9; padding-top: 15px; }
        .avatar { width: 35px; height: 35px; background: #eee; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; }

        /* --- INFO & PATIČKA --- */
        footer { background: #1d1d1f; color: #fff; padding: 50px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
        .funko-info { color: #86868b; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #333; padding-top: 20px; }

        /* --- RESPONSIVITA (MOBIL) --- */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .logo { font-size: 24px; }
            .review-card { padding: 20px; }
            .rating-summary h2 { font-size: 36px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">VUCAOFOODS</div>
        <p>Vaše lokální potraviny v Košířích</p>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="brands-section">
    <div class="brands-title">Značky, které u nás najdete</div>
    <div class="slider-track">
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="vilgain">vilgain</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="sufan">Šufan</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="druid">Druid</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="gingles">Gingles</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="vinarstvi">Vinařství Hodonín</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="prosekarna">Prosekárna</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="vilgain">vilgain</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="sufan">Šufan</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="druid">Druid</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="gingles">Gingles</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="vinarstvi">Vinařství Hodonín</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
        <div class="partner-item"><span class="prosekarna">Prosekárna</span><div class="separator"></div></div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="reviews-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="rating-summary">
            <h2>5,0</h2>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p>26 recenzí na Google Maps</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reviews-grid">
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="review-text">"Konečně super obchod! Je nově otevřený, majitel je moc fajn, otevřeno celý den a skvělý sortiment."</p>
                <div class="reviewer">
                    <div class="avatar">JJ</div>
                    <div><b>Jakub Jirovec</b></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="review-text">"Nově otevřen obchod. Zatím jsem koupil vždy vše co jsem potřeboval. Obsluha je příjemná."</p>
                <div class="reviewer">
                    <div class="avatar">RN</div>
                    <div><b>Robert Nguyen</b></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <div class="container">
        <p><b>VUCAOFOODS</b> | Plzeňská, Praha - Košíře</p>
        <p>Otevřeno denně: 07:00 – 21:00</p>
        
        <div class="funko-info">
            Výrobce Funko: Funko LLC, distribuční centrum Funko EU BV, Zuidplein 36, 1077 XV, Amsterdam, Nizozemsko.
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
